<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Diagnóstico de Necesidades IA — Innogyzer</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&display=swap');

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --blue-dark:   #1A478A;
    --blue-mid:    #2E7DD1;
    --blue-light:  #D6E8F8;
    --blue-xlight: #EEF6FD;
    --blue-accent: #4FA3E8;
    --white:       #FFFFFF;
    --gray-100:    #F7FAFD;
    --gray-200:    #E8EFF7;
    --gray-500:    #6B7A99;
    --gray-800:    #1E2A3B;
    --success:     #1A6B3C;
    --error:       #C0392B;
    --radius:      10px;
    --shadow:      0 2px 16px rgba(26,71,138,.10);
    --transition:  .18s ease;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    color: var(--gray-800);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
  }

  /* ── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  header {
    background: var(--blue-dark);
    padding: 18px 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
  }
  header .logo {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -.3px;
  }
  header .logo span { color: var(--blue-accent); }
  header .tagline { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); margin-top: 2px; }

  /* ── Hero ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-dark) 0%, #1d5fa8 60%, var(--blue-mid) 100%);
    padding: 52px 32px 44px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Ccircle cx='30' cy='30' r='2'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }
  .hero-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--blue-accent); }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.75);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── Progress bar ────────────────────────────────────── */
  .progress-wrap {
    background: var(--blue-dark);
    padding: 0 32px 20px;
  }
  .progress-steps {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .progress-steps .step {
    flex: 1;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.2);
    transition: background var(--transition);
  }
  .progress-steps .step.active { background: var(--blue-accent); }
  .progress-steps .step.done   { background: rgba(255,255,255,.5); }

  /* ── Main container ──────────────────────────────────── */
  main {
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 16px 0;
  }

  /* ── Form sections ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .form-section {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
  }

  .section-header {
    background: var(--blue-dark);
    padding: 14px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .section-header .num {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    width: 24px; height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .section-header .sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .section-body { padding: 20px 24px; }

  /* ── Field groups ────────────────────────────────────── */
  .field-group {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .field-group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .field-group label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: .2px;
  }
  .field-group .hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  input[type="text"],
  input[type="email"],
  input[type="tel"],
  input[type="url"],
  select,
  textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px 13px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
    border-radius: 7px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    background: var(--gray-100);
    transition: border-color var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
    outline: none;
  }
  input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--blue-mid);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(46,125,209,.12);
    background: #fff;
  }
  textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 90px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── Question block (checkboxes) ─────────────────────── */
  .question-block {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .question-block:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .question-label {
    background: var(--blue-xlight);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blue-light);
  }

  .options-list { padding: 4px 0; }

  .option-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 9px 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background var(--transition);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    position: relative;
  }
  .option-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .option-item:hover { background: var(--blue-xlight); }
  .option-item:nth-child(even) { background: var(--gray-100); }
  .option-item:nth-child(even):hover { background: var(--blue-xlight); }

  .option-item input[type="checkbox"],
  .option-item input[type="radio"] {
    width: 16px; height: 16px;
    min-width: 16px;
    margin-top: 1px;
    accent-color: var(--blue-mid);
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    background: transparent;
    box-shadow: none;
  }
  .option-item input:focus { box-shadow: none; }

  .option-item span {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    line-height: 1.45;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .option-item input:checked + span {
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  /* checked row highlight */
  .option-item:has(input:checked) {
    background: var(--blue-light) !important;
  }

  /* ── Divider ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gray-200);
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  /* ── Submit button ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .submit-wrap {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8px 0 32px;
  }
  .btn-submit {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-dark), var(--blue-mid));
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 15px 48px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(26,71,138,.3);
    letter-spacing: .2px;
  }
  .btn-submit:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(26,71,138,.4);
  }
  .btn-submit:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .btn-submit:disabled { opacity: .6; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }

  .submit-note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  /* ── Success / Error state ───────────────────────────── */
  .alert {
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: none;
  }
  .alert.success { background: #E8F5EE; color: var(--success); border: 1px solid #A8D5BC; }
  .alert.error   { background: #FDF0EF; color: var(--error);   border: 1px solid #EBB0AA; }
  .alert.show    { display: block; }

  /* ── Footer ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 28px 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--blue-mid); text-decoration: none; }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    header { padding: 14px 16px; }
    .hero { padding: 36px 16px 32px; }
    .progress-wrap { padding: 0 16px 16px; }
    .section-body { padding: 16px; }
    .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; }
  }

  /* ── Claude section ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .claude-section {
    border: 1.5px solid #C8DCEF;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(46,125,209,.13);
  }
  .claude-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A478A 0%, #1d6db5 60%, #2E7DD1 100%) !important;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .claude-header::after {
    content: '✦ ANTHROPIC PARTNER';
    position: absolute;
    right: -28px; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(90deg);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .claude-num {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.25) !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4);
  }
  .claude-badge {
    margin-left: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.9);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .claude-intro {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--blue-xlight);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blue-light);
    padding: 14px 24px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .claude-intro-icon {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--blue-mid);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .claude-disclaimer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    background: #F0F7FF;
    border: 1px solid var(--blue-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 11px 14px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--blue-dark);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-top: 18px;
  }
  .claude-disclaimer svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Header -->
<header>
  <div>
    <div class="logo">Inno<span>gyzer</span></div>
    <div class="tagline">The AI Sprint Innovation Agency</div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Hero -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-pill">⚡ Diagnóstico gratuito</div>
  <h1>Dinos qué quieres lograr<br>con <em>IA</em> y lo construimos</h1>
  <p>Leads · Automatización · Hiperpersonalización<br>
  Este formulario nos ayuda a entender tu situación y prepararte una propuesta a la medida.</p>
</div>

<!-- Progress -->
<div class="progress-wrap">
  <div class="progress-steps" id="progressSteps">
    <div class="step active" id="s1"></div>
    <div class="step" id="s2"></div>
    <div class="step" id="s3"></div>
    <div class="step" id="s4"></div>
    <div class="step" id="s5"></div>
    <div class="step" id="s6"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Main -->
<main>

  <div id="alertBox" class="alert"></div>

  <form id="briefForm" novalidate>

    <!-- ══ 1. DATOS ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h2>Tus datos de contacto</h2>
          <div class="sub">Nos ayuda a personalizar tu propuesta</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="empresa">Empresa *</label>
            <input type="text" id="empresa" name="empresa" placeholder="Nombre de tu empresa" required>
          </div>
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="fecha">Fecha</label>
            <input type="text" id="fecha" name="fecha" readonly
              style="background:#f0f5fb;color:var(--gray-500);cursor:default;">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="nombre">Nombre y cargo *</label>
            <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Tu nombre — Director de Marketing" required>
          </div>
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="email">Correo electrónico *</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="tu@empresa.com" required>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="whatsapp">WhatsApp / Teléfono</label>
            <input type="tel" id="whatsapp" name="whatsapp" placeholder="+52 55 0000 0000">
          </div>
          <div class="field-group">
            <label for="industria">Industria / Sector</label>
            <select id="industria" name="industria">
              <option value="">Selecciona...</option>
              <option>BPO / Contact Center</option>
              <option>Banca y Finanzas</option>
              <option>Seguros</option>
              <option>Retail y E-commerce</option>
              <option>Salud</option>
              <option>Educación</option>
              <option>Tecnología / SaaS</option>
              <option>Manufactura</option>
              <option>Agencia de marketing</option>
              <option>Otro</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ══ 2. SITUACIÓN ACTUAL ════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h2>Situación actual</h2>
          <div class="sub">Cómo operan hoy en generación de leads y marketing</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-body">

        <div class="question-block">
          <div class="question-label">¿Cómo generan leads hoy? (selecciona todos los que apliquen)</div>
          <div class="options-list">
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="gen_leads[]" value="pauta_digital"><span>Pauta digital (Meta Ads, Google Ads, TikTok Ads)</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="gen_leads[]" value="equipo_comercial"><span>Equipo comercial / prospección manual</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="gen_leads[]" value="inbound_organico"><span>Inbound / contenido orgánico (SEO, redes sociales)</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="gen_leads[]" value="eventos_webinars"><span>Eventos, webinars o alianzas</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="gen_leads[]" value="base_datos_propia"><span>Base de datos propia (email, WhatsApp, CRM)</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="gen_leads[]" value="referidos"><span>Referidos / boca en boca</span></label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="question-block">
          <div class="question-label">¿Qué tan automatizados están sus flujos de marketing y ventas?</div>
          <div class="options-list">
            <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="nivel_automatizacion" value="nada"><span>Nada — todo es manual</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="nivel_automatizacion" value="algo"><span>Algo — tenemos algunos correos o secuencias básicas</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="nivel_automatizacion" value="moderado"><span>Moderado — usamos CRM y flujos, pero no con IA</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="nivel_automatizacion" value="avanzado"><span>Avanzado — ya automatizamos bastante, queremos el siguiente nivel</span></label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="field-group">
            <label>¿Cuántos leads generan al mes? (aprox.)</label>
            <select name="vol_leads">
              <option value="">Selecciona...</option>
              <option>Menos de 100</option>
              <option>100 – 500</option>
              <option>500 – 2,000</option>
              <option>2,000 – 10,000</option>
              <option>Más de 10,000</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="field-group">
            <label>Tasa de conversión actual (aprox.)</label>
            <select name="tasa_conversion">
              <option value="">Selecciona...</option>
              <option>Menos del 1%</option>
              <option>1% – 3%</option>
              <option>3% – 7%</option>
              <option>Más del 7%</option>
              <option>No la medimos</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="field-group">
            <label>Herramientas actuales (CRM, email, pauta...)</label>
            <input type="text" name="herramientas_actuales" placeholder="HubSpot, Mailchimp, Meta Ads...">
          </div>
          <div class="field-group">
            <label>Inversión mensual en publicidad digital (aprox.)</label>
            <select name="inversion_pauta">
              <option value="">Selecciona...</option>
              <option>Menos de $10,000 MXN</option>
              <option>$10,000 – $50,000 MXN</option>
              <option>$50,000 – $200,000 MXN</option>
              <option>Más de $200,000 MXN</option>
              <option>No invertimos en pauta</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ══ 3. RETOS Y OPORTUNIDADES ═══════════════════════ -->
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h2>Retos y oportunidades</h2>
          <div class="sub">Tus principales retos y las oportunidades que ves</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-body">

        <div class="question-block">
          <div class="question-label">¿Cuál es el mayor problema en tu proceso de leads hoy? (marca los 3 más importantes)</div>
          <div class="options-list">
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="poco_volumen"><span>Generamos pocos leads — necesitamos más volumen</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="baja_calidad"><span>Los leads que llegan no son de calidad o no califican</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="seguimiento_lento"><span>El seguimiento es lento o inconsistente</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="baja_conversion"><span>Tenemos leads pero no los convertimos bien</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="no_saber_creativos"><span>No sabemos qué mensajes o creativos funcionan antes de invertir</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="sin_personalizacion"><span>Cada lead recibe el mismo mensaje — sin personalización</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="sin_visibilidad"><span>No tenemos visibilidad de qué canal genera los mejores resultados</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="mkt_ventas_desconectado"><span>El proceso entre marketing y ventas está desconectado</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="respuesta_lenta"><span>Perdemos leads por falta de respuesta rápida</span></label>
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="problemas[]" value="base_no_aprovechada"><span>No aprovechamos la base de datos que ya tenemos</span></label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="question-block">
          <div class="question-label">¿Qué oportunidad ves con IA que hoy no estás aprovechando?</div>
          <div class="options-list">
            <label class="option-item"><input type="checkbox" name="oportunidades[]" value="personalizacion_mensajes"><span>Personalizar mensajes y creativos para cada segmento o cliente</span></label>
